{"tid":1730553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有能力嘅唔該出黎反包圍救理大","createTime":"2019-11-17T13:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T04:07:30.000Z","uid":291448,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"aafe980a99f764dcda5c2d8045a8e431127790d6","tid":1730553,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:58:14.000Z","msg":"認真 而家理大已經到左最危險嘅時刻  入面嘅手足已經走唔到出去 所有出口已經封死晒<br />\n若果最終理大比班黑警成功攻左入去 後果一定不堪設想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班黑警一定會攞手足黎洩憤 男嘅會被毒打一身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女嘅就被輪姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以如果大家而家可以過嚟幫到手嘅就黎幫手 <br />\n過黎理大反包圍班狗  等佢地知難而退<br />\n同埋可以黎個各區開花  <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">紅土 尖沙咀 旺角 深水埗  Set RB等..分散警力</span></strong><br />\n咁樣理大就會有救啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f704e6d08a0d7f973825463e49211d27c7fb7739","tid":1730553,"uid":259963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求大家救救poly<br />\n班黑警已經唔理開花架啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">油尖旺嘅手足麻煩反包返黑警</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其他區就開花燒狗宿狗屋狗車</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已經出曬槍同埋趕記者走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該真係要救救理大"},{"pid":"285b6c72080bd2bfd4a46c188ceed8663580a149","tid"